1. Džon je otišao na sahranu svoje bake. (*sahranu*) (John went to his grandmother's funeral.)
2. Posle sahrane, svi su otišli u restoran da bi se okrepili. (*sahrane*) (After the funeral, everyone went to the restaurant to refresh themselves.)
3. Nije pristojno fotografisati se na sahrani. (*sahrani*) (It's not polite to take photos at a funeral.)
4. Mnogo ljudi je došlo da izjavi saučešće porodici nakon sahrane. (*nakon sahrane*) (Many people came to express their condolences to the family after the funeral.)
5. Moram da kupim novu crnu haljinu za sahranu. (*za sahranu*) (I need to buy a new black dress for the funeral.)
6. Dejan je prekinuo godišnji odmor zbog sahrane svog ujaka. (*zbog sahrane*) (Dejan interrupted his vacation because of his uncle's funeral.)
7. Pre sahrane, svi su stajali u redu da bi izrazili saučešće porodici. (*pre sahrane*) (Before the funeral, everyone stood in line to express their condolences to the family.)
8. Nakon sahrane, majka je plakala danima. (*nakon sahrane*) (After the funeral, the mother cried for days.)
9. Ana je donela cveće na sahranu svoje drugarice. (*na sahranu*) (Ana brought flowers to her friend's funeral.)
10. Nikola nije otišao na sahranu svoje tetke, ali je poslao telegram saučešća. (*na sahranu*) (Nikola didn't go to his aunt's funeral, but he sent a condolence telegram.)